sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Note the browser stores the new note locally and sends a request to get confirmation that the server has thereceived the new data. 

    browser->>server: POST 	https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    server-->>browser: JSON - {"message":"note created"}
